  "title": "Issue with button & ais-refinement-list",
  "body": "Hi! I'm currently working with algolia/instantsearch and i would like checkbox buttons so i wrote this code : \r\n```\r\n<ais-refinement-list attribute-name=\"Source_type\" :type=\"checkbox\">\r\n</ais-refinement-list>\r\n```\r\nbut i have this in return : \r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/31215695/29663352-edf7a6dc-88ca-11e7-932d-5baa9dfb5d68.png)\r\n\r\nI'm suspecting a \"-webkit-appearance\" fault? Because when i'm in my console and i untick '-webkit-appearance=none' it worked...but when i deleted it in my  .css it didn't.\r\nIf you have any ideas or solutions ? Thank you. ",
